            <input type="radio" id="q8a" name="q8" value="2000">
            <label for="q8a">2000</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q8b" name="q8" value="8000">
            <label for="q8b">8000</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q8c" name="q8" value="14000">
            <label for="q8c">14000</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q8d" name="q8" value="10000">
            <label for="q8d">10000</label><br>

            

            <li>How many votes does one roll constitute?</li>
            <input type="radio" id="q9a" name="q9" value="1">
            <label for="q9a">1</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q9b" name="q9" value="2">
            <label for="q9b">2</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q9c" name="q9" value="3">
            <label for="q9c">3</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q9d" name="q9" value="4">
            <label for="q9d">4</label><br>


            <li>How long does a cycle last?</li>
            <input type="radio" id="q10a" name="q10" value="1048 blocks">
            <label for="q10a">1048 blocks</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q10b" name="q10" value="2196 blocks">
            <label for="q10b">2196 blocks</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q10c" name="q10" value="4096 blocks">
            <label for="q10c">4096 blocks</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q10d" name="q10" value="2048 blocks">
            <label for="q10d">2048 blocks</label><br>

           

            <li>Name the first Tezos on-chain upgrade proposal.</li>
            <input type="radio" id="q11a" name="q11" value="Athens A">
            <label for="q11a">Athens A</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q11b" name="q11" value="Babylon">
            <label for="q11b">Babylon</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q11c" name="q11" value="Carthage">
            <label for="q11c">Carthage</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q11d" name="q11" value="Athens B">
            <label for="q11d">Athens B</label><br>

            <li>Which govt. organisation uses Tezos smart contracts? </li>
            <input type="radio" id="q12a" name="q12" value="Indian Space Research Organisation">
            <label for="q12a">Indian Space Research Organisation</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q12b" name="q12" value="Department of homeland security, USA">
            <label for="q12b">Department of homeland security, USA</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q12c" name="q12" value="French cyber crime division, The Gendarmerie Nationale (Cybercrime Centre)">
            <label for="q12c">French cyber crime division, The Gendarmerie Nationale (Cybercrime Centre)</label><br>
            <input type="radio" id="q12d" name="q12" value="The Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation">
            <label for="q12d">The Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation</label><br>
        </ol>
